{"tid":1628173,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一早講左比人帶緊風向咩鋪頭都爆","createTime":"2019-10-06T01:11:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T04:37:19.000Z","uid":4236,"like":61,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"be44a4fc8e089400fac8d5b86be39678b2c69acb","tid":1628173,"uid":4236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T01:11:25.000Z","msg":"無可否認、成個連登比人帶緊風向去爆鋪頭。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1615141\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1615141</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n成個post好多屌我既人都係出曬名既五毛黎<br />\n唔介意自己入去睇下 仲有成班屌我左膠既人<br />\n你地比五毛利用左啦柒頭 仲係度撐佢地<br />\n人地個策略就係要你地咩都爆<br />\n然後不斷宣傳 再要和理非同暴力割 成個策略明顯到咁 點解可以咁蠢？ 好啦依家衝動累事 又道歉又剩 <br />\n另外爆乜撚野特許經營姐其實 入去坐同貼連儂咪得囉 一樣咁大影響 <br />\n我點都唔會割 你都係 但唔該脫離下同溫層望下 大家都對裝修冷處理緊 除左福建幫旗下之外 大家都唔割但唔代表咩都認同啊柒頭<br />\n根本裝修就要有一個原則同共識係度 咁咪唔使又裝修錯然後道歉囉<br />\nps我已經被歸類為鬼同左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b6aaebb499d72c933e3dee41bd65e61a61e6c1a","tid":1628173,"uid":4236,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T01:14:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e6b8a5ec7f551607adae66e4049ee8b6c4a17cc","tid":1628173,"uid":4236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T01:16:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae536574304e64f5fd1a483ba21e13261ab3472